1. Go on your Player and add the XROrigin script or the XRRig script in the missing script

2. Go inside and click on GorillaPlayer, in the missing script add the LocomotionSystem script and select the Player with the XROrigin or XRRig script

3. On the turning script under the LocomotionSystem add the LocomotionSystem Object

4. Go inside GorillaPlayer and TurnParent and on Main Camera in the missing script add the top Tracked Pose Driver

5. Go on Left and Right Hand Controller and add the XRController script and on the Left Hand Controller make sure you change a option from Right to Left
